import React from "react";
import * as AiIcons from 'react-icons/ai';
import * as RiIcons from 'react-icons/ri'

const IconStyle = {
    width:"40px",
    height:"40px", 
    marginRight:'15px',
    color: '#fff',
    image:''
}

export const CardsData = [
    {
        heading : "Nouvelle Demande",
        icon:<AiIcons.AiFillFileAdd style={IconStyle}/>,
        number:null,
        path:'nouvelle-demande',
        color:'linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(83,32,186,1) 12%, rgba(128,131,194,1) 100%)',
        image:''
    },
    {
        heading : "En Verification", 
        icon:<AiIcons.AiOutlineFileSync style={IconStyle}/>,
        number:0,
        color:'#fff',
        path:'en-verification',
        color:'#A2D4F2',
        image:''
    },
    {
        heading : "À completer",
        icon:<RiIcons.RiFileChart2Fill style={IconStyle}/>,
        number:0,
        color:'#fff',
        path:'a-completer',
        color:'#FAC699',
        image:''
    },
    {
        heading : "Dossier Traités",
        icon:<AiIcons.AiOutlineFileDone style={IconStyle}/>,
        number:0,
        color:'#fff',
        path:'dossier-traites',
        color:'#B3E3B6',
        image:''
    },
    {
        heading : "Refusés",
        icon:<AiIcons.AiFillFileExcel style={IconStyle}/>,
        number:0,
        color:'#fff',
        path:'refuses',
        color:'#D991AB',
        image:''
    }
    
]
